{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01B8mnjTvTQtsNa3ZEvvAPWv","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have a comprehensive understanding of the project. Let me create a detailed summary report.\n\n## AxenWP Project Exploration - Complete Analysis\n\nI've thoroughly explored the AxenWP project. Here's the comprehensive overview:\n\n---\n\n### 1. DIRECTORY STRUCTURE\n\n**Root Files:**\n- `/main.py` - FastAPI entry point (147 lines)\n- `/requirements.txt` - Python dependencies\n- `/alembic.ini` - Alembic migration config\n- `/docker-compose.yml` - Docker deployment\n- `/Dockerfile` - Container definition\n- `/.env.example` - Environment template\n- `/README.md` - Documentation\n\n**Key Directories:**\n- `/admin/` - Admin dashboard & AI agent management\n  - `dashboard.py` - Admin UI (Jinja2 templates + authentication)\n  - `ai_agent.py` - AI agent API endpoints (448 lines)\n  \n- `/services/` - Business logic\n  - `ai_service.py` - LangChain + OpenRouter AI engine (326 lines)\n  - `ghl_service.py` - GoHighLevel CRM integration (355 lines)\n  - `zapi_service.py` - Z-API WhatsApp integration (237 lines)\n  \n- `/auth/` - Authentication & token management\n  - `token_manager.py` - OAuth token lifecycle\n  - `oauth.py` - OAuth 2.0 flow\n  \n- `/webhooks/` - Webhook receivers\n  - `zapi_receiver.py` - Z-API inbound messages (403 lines)\n  - `ghl_provider.py` - GHL outbound webhook handler (355 lines)\n  \n- `/data/` - Data models & database\n  - `models.py` - SQLAlchemy ORM models (154 lines)\n  - `database.py` - Database configuration\n  \n- `/utils/` - Utilities\n  - `config.py` - Settings from .env (pydantic)\n  - `logger.py` - Logging setup\n  \n- `/alembic/versions/` - Database migrations\n  - `001_add_missing_columns.py` - Initial schema + system_settings table\n  - `002_add_debounce_seconds.py` - AI agent debounce config\n  - `003_add_groq_api_key.py` - Groq Whisper for audio transcription\n  - `004_add_elevenlabs_voice_settings.py` - ElevenLabs voice parameters\n  \n- `/web/` - Frontend\n  - `/templates/` - Jinja2 templates (dashboard.html, login.html)\n  - `/static/` - CSS/JS/images\n  \n- `/alembic/` - Migration management\n- `/scripts/` - Utility scripts\n- `.ralph/` - Ralph AI agent development files (DO NOT MODIFY)\n\n**Total Python Files:** 6036 (including venv)\n\n---\n\n### 2. RECENT GIT HISTORY (Last 15 commits)\n\n```\n891fa3b - fix(security): restrict CORS origins via ALLOWED_ORIGINS env var\n78aa099 - refactor(master-ai): 3-step approach to prevent truncated/abbreviated prompts\n6ed7b3a - fix(master-ai): fix truncated/incomplete prompt improvements\ned163cc - fix(memory): fix chat history not being used by LLM\nad80661 - chore: remove unused Tuple import from ai_service.py\n1b77282 - feat(voice): add ElevenLabs voice settings (speed, stability, similarity)\n37853b0 - fix(audio): use OGG Opus format for WhatsApp voice messages with waveforms\n1de9b70 - fix(audio): persist groq_api_key in dashboard + replace always_reply toggle with smart mode\ne81dba1 - feat(audio): add STT transcription via Groq Whisper + fix audio send/receive flow\n0b4017a - upp\n911e32d - upp\na8af992 - up\n95db7c2 - add\nfc9648b - feat(tester): add Master AI simulation button in Tester tab\n2058d78 - feat(master-chat): add iterative feedback chat with Master AI\n```\n\n**Current Branch:** `ralph/tasks`\n**Main Branch:** `main`\n\n---\n\n### 3. DATABASE SCHEMA (SQLAlchemy Models)\n\n**Tables:**\n\n1. **tenants** - Multi-tenant company data\n   - location_id (PK), company_name, client_id, client_secret\n   - access_token, refresh_token, token_expires_at\n   - zapi_instance_id, zapi_token, zapi_client_token\n   - conversation_provider_id, is_active, created_at\n\n2. **ai_agents** - AI configuration per tenant\n   - id (PK), location_id (FK, unique), name, prompt, model\n   - api_key (OpenRouter), elevenlabs_api_key, elevenlabs_voice_id\n   - elevenlabs_speed, elevenlabs_stability, elevenlabs_similarity\n   - groq_api_key (for Whisper), is_active, debounce_seconds\n   - created_at, updated_at\n\n3. **knowledge_documents** - Knowledge base files\n   - id (PK), tenant_id (FK), filename, file_type, blob_url, is_indexed\n   - created_at, updated_at\n\n4. **chat_histories** - Chat memory for AI conversations\n   - id (PK), session_id, message_type (human/ai/system), content\n   - created_at\n\n5. **contact_mappings** - Phone → GHL contact ID mapping\n   - id (PK), location_id, phone_or_lid, ghl_contact_id, created_at\n\n6. **message_mappings** - Z-API messageId ↔ GHL messageId\n   - zapi_message_id (PK), ghl_message_id, location_id, status\n   - created_at\n\n7. **system_settings** - Global system configuration\n   - id (PK), admin_openrouter_key, admin_openrouter_model, updated_at\n\n---\n\n### 4. DEPENDENCIES (requirements.txt)\n\n```\nfastapi==0.115.0\nuvicorn[standard]==0.30.0\nhttpx==0.27.0\napscheduler==3.10.4\npython-dotenv==1.0.1\npydantic>=2.9.0\npydantic-settings>=2.10.1\njinja2==3.1.4\npython-multipart==0.0.9\nsqlalchemy==2.0.35\nalembic==1.13.3\npsycopg2-binary>=2.9.9\nlangchain==1.2.10\nlangchain-classic==1.0.2\nlangchain-community==0.4.1\nlangchain-core==1.2.17\nlangchain-openai==1.1.10\nlangchain-text-splitters==1.1.1\n```\n\n**Stack Summary:**\n- Backend: FastAPI + Uvicorn\n- Database: PostgreSQL (psycopg2-binary)\n- Migrations: Alembic\n- ORM: SQLAlchemy 2.0\n- AI/LLM: LangChain + OpenRouter\n- Voice: ElevenLabs (TTS), Groq Whisper (STT)\n- WhatsApp: Z-API\n- CRM: GoHighLevel\n- Async HTTP: httpx\n\n---\n\n### 5. KEY FEATURES & IMPLEMENTATION DETAILS\n\n**Authentication & Multi-Tenancy:**\n- OAuth 2.0 flow with GHL (GoHighLevel)\n- Token auto-refresh every 12 hours via APScheduler\n- Cookie-based admin dashboard authentication\n\n**AI Agent Engine:**\n- LangChain + ChatOpenAI via OpenRouter\n- PostgreSQL-backed chat memory (PostgresChatMessageHistory)\n- Prompt improvement system (3-step Master AI)\n- Audio transcription via Groq Whisper (STT)\n- Audio response via ElevenLabs (TTS) with configurable voice settings\n- Smart fallback: audio→text if response contains special content (URLs, R$, CPF, etc.)\n- Debounce mechanism: combines rapid messages before AI processing\n\n**Webhook Flows:**\n1. **GHL → Z-API (Outbound):** Message sent in GHL → forwarded to WhatsApp via Z-API\n2. **Z-API → GHL (Inbound):** WhatsApp message received → processed by AI agent → response sent back to GHL\n\n**Dashboard:**\n- Admin login with HMAC-based session tokens\n- Tenant management\n- AI agent configuration (prompt, model, keys, voice settings)\n- Prompt analyzer & improvement with Master AI\n- Chat tester for live agent testing\n- Master AI iterative feedback chat\n\n---\n\n### 6. ISSUES, OBSERVATIONS & POTENTIAL PROBLEMS\n\n**Positive Aspects:**\n- Clean separation of concerns (routers, services, data layers)\n- Proper error handling with try/finally blocks\n- Idempotent database migrations using `_column_exists()` checks\n- Type hints throughout (Python 3.10+ annotations)\n- Environment configuration via pydantic-settings\n\n**Observations & Potential Issues:**\n\n1. **CORS Configuration Warning** (main.py:85-90)\n   - If `ALLOWED_ORIGINS` is not set and `DEBUG=false`, CORS will block cross-origin requests\n   - Current code logs warning but still permits all origins if DEBUG=true\n\n2. **No Test Files Found**\n   - No `tests/` directory or `test_*.py` files in the codebase\n   - No test instructions in `.ralph/AGENT.md` (marked \"No test command configured\")\n\n3. **Chat History Architecture**\n   - Uses SQLAlchemy directly in `PostgresChatMessageHistory` (not async)\n   - Loads full history synchronously during AI request processing\n   - Could be bottleneck with large conversation histories\n\n4. **Session Management**\n   - Admin dashboard uses simple HMAC cookie token (no expiration handling visible)\n   - Cookie max_age set to 30 days\n\n5. **Error Handling Patterns**\n   - Some endpoints use `return` instead of raising HTTPException\n   - Inconsistent error response formats across endpoints\n\n6. **File Organization**\n   - `template_agenteia/` directory exists but purpose unclear\n   - `scripts/` directory exists but content not examined\n\n7. **Migrations Chain**\n   - Migration 004 (ElevenLabs voice settings) exists but not yet reviewed in models.py\n   - All migrations use safe idempotent patterns\n\n8. **Async/Await Usage**\n   - Main.py runs sync Alembic operations in async context (during lifespan)\n   - ChatHistory uses sync SessionLocal in async AI engine\n\n9. **No Type Annotations in Some Places**\n   - Some Pydantic models in admin/ai_agent.py use basic BaseModel without field validation\n\n10. **README.md Notes**\n    - Documentation references `/data/tenants/*.json` but current schema uses database\n    - README may be outdated relative to current PostgreSQL-based implementation\n\n---\n\n### 7. MAIN.PY STRUCTURE\n\n```\n1. Imports (FastAPI, middleware, schedulers, routes)\n2. APScheduler setup for token refresh\n3. Lifespan context manager:\n   - Create all tables via SQLAlchemy\n   - Apply Alembic migrations\n   - Start scheduler\n   - Run initial token refresh\n4. FastAPI app instantiation with CORS configuration\n5. Route registration (5 routers)\n6. Static file mounting\n7. Health endpoints: `/`, `/health`\n8. Uvicorn runner\n```\n\n---\n\n### 8. ALEMBIC MIGRATIONS STATUS\n\n**Current Chain (HEAD → 004):**\n\n| ID | Description | Safe | Status |\n|----|-------------|------|--------|\n| 001 | Add missing columns + system_settings | Idempotent | Applied |\n| 002 | Add debounce_seconds | Idempotent | Applied |\n| 003 | Add groq_api_key | Idempotent | Applied |\n| 004 | Add ElevenLabs voice settings | Not reviewed | Pending |\n\nAll migrations use `_column_exists()` and `_table_exists()` helper functions for safety.\n\n---\n\n### 9. ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES (.env.example)\n\n```\nGHL_CLIENT_ID, GHL_CLIENT_SECRET, GHL_REDIRECT_URI\nGHL_CONVERSATION_PROVIDER_ID\nDATABASE_URL (postgresql://...)\nHOST, PORT\nZAPI_WEBHOOK_SECRET\nLOG_LEVEL\nALLOWED_ORIGINS (NEW - for CORS)\nDEBUG (NEW - for security & reload)\n```\n\n---\n\n### 10. CURRENT STATE & RECOMMENDATIONS\n\n**Health Status:** HEALTHY with minor observations\n\n**Recently Fixed Issues (from git history):**\n- CORS security restriction via env var ✓\n- Master AI prompt truncation issues ✓\n- Chat history not being used by LLM ✓\n- Audio STT/TTS flows ✓\n\n**Recommended Next Actions:**\n1. Add comprehensive test suite for core services\n2. Document the 004 migration (ElevenLabs settings)\n3. Review async/sync boundary issues in ChatHistory loading\n4. Update README.md with current database architecture\n5. Consider adding request validation in Pydantic models\n6. Add integration tests for webhook flows\n\n---\n\n**Files Summary:**\n- Total Python files (excluding venv): ~40 core files\n- Largest files: zapi_receiver.py (403 lines), ghl_service.py (355 lines), ai_service.py (326 lines)\n- Total commits: 15 recent (active development, mostly features + security fixes)\n- Current branch: ralph/tasks (AI agent working on improvements)"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: ae3810c415059ef65 (use SendMessage with to: 'ae3810c415059ef65' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 58770\ntool_uses: 47\nduration_ms: 70850</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e47418a4-c150-4f43-895d-86d1b02f5994","uuid":"9b256600-c519-4f40-aa19-760433d20e8a","timestamp":"2026-03-20T16:38:55.703Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Explore the AxenWP project thoroughly. I need to understand:\n\n1. The overall directory structure (list key files and folders)\n2. Recent git log (last 15 commits with messages)\n3. Any TODO/FIXME/HACK comments in the codebase\n4. The current state of main.py, services/ai_service.py, and any test files\n5. Check if there's a requirements.txt or pyproject.toml\n6. Look for any obvious issues, missing imports, or broken code patterns\n7. Check the alembic migrations directory for current state\n\nBe thorough - I need a complete picture of what's happening in this project.","agentId":"ae3810c415059ef65","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have a comprehensive understanding of the project. Let me create a detailed summary report.\n\n## AxenWP Project Exploration - Complete Analysis\n\nI've thoroughly explored the AxenWP project. Here's the comprehensive overview:\n\n---\n\n### 1. DIRECTORY STRUCTURE\n\n**Root Files:**\n- `/main.py` - FastAPI entry point (147 lines)\n- `/requirements.txt` - Python dependencies\n- `/alembic.ini` - Alembic migration config\n- `/docker-compose.yml` - Docker deployment\n- `/Dockerfile` - Container definition\n- `/.env.example` - Environment template\n- `/README.md` - Documentation\n\n**Key Directories:**\n- `/admin/` - Admin dashboard & AI agent management\n  - `dashboard.py` - Admin UI (Jinja2 templates + authentication)\n  - `ai_agent.py` - AI agent API endpoints (448 lines)\n  \n- `/services/` - Business logic\n  - `ai_service.py` - LangChain + OpenRouter AI engine (326 lines)\n  - `ghl_service.py` - GoHighLevel CRM integration (355 lines)\n  - `zapi_service.py` - Z-API WhatsApp integration (237 lines)\n  \n- `/auth/` - Authentication & token management\n  - `token_manager.py` - OAuth token lifecycle\n  - `oauth.py` - OAuth 2.0 flow\n  \n- `/webhooks/` - Webhook receivers\n  - `zapi_receiver.py` - Z-API inbound messages (403 lines)\n  - `ghl_provider.py` - GHL outbound webhook handler (355 lines)\n  \n- `/data/` - Data models & database\n  - `models.py` - SQLAlchemy ORM models (154 lines)\n  - `database.py` - Database configuration\n  \n- `/utils/` - Utilities\n  - `config.py` - Settings from .env (pydantic)\n  - `logger.py` - Logging setup\n  \n- `/alembic/versions/` - Database migrations\n  - `001_add_missing_columns.py` - Initial schema + system_settings table\n  - `002_add_debounce_seconds.py` - AI agent debounce config\n  - `003_add_groq_api_key.py` - Groq Whisper for audio transcription\n  - `004_add_elevenlabs_voice_settings.py` - ElevenLabs voice parameters\n  \n- `/web/` - Frontend\n  - `/templates/` - Jinja2 templates (dashboard.html, login.html)\n  - `/static/` - CSS/JS/images\n  \n- `/alembic/` - Migration management\n- `/scripts/` - Utility scripts\n- `.ralph/` - Ralph AI agent development files (DO NOT MODIFY)\n\n**Total Python Files:** 6036 (including venv)\n\n---\n\n### 2. RECENT GIT HISTORY (Last 15 commits)\n\n```\n891fa3b - fix(security): restrict CORS origins via ALLOWED_ORIGINS env var\n78aa099 - refactor(master-ai): 3-step approach to prevent truncated/abbreviated prompts\n6ed7b3a - fix(master-ai): fix truncated/incomplete prompt improvements\ned163cc - fix(memory): fix chat history not being used by LLM\nad80661 - chore: remove unused Tuple import from ai_service.py\n1b77282 - feat(voice): add ElevenLabs voice settings (speed, stability, similarity)\n37853b0 - fix(audio): use OGG Opus format for WhatsApp voice messages with waveforms\n1de9b70 - fix(audio): persist groq_api_key in dashboard + replace always_reply toggle with smart mode\ne81dba1 - feat(audio): add STT transcription via Groq Whisper + fix audio send/receive flow\n0b4017a - upp\n911e32d - upp\na8af992 - up\n95db7c2 - add\nfc9648b - feat(tester): add Master AI simulation button in Tester tab\n2058d78 - feat(master-chat): add iterative feedback chat with Master AI\n```\n\n**Current Branch:** `ralph/tasks`\n**Main Branch:** `main`\n\n---\n\n### 3. DATABASE SCHEMA (SQLAlchemy Models)\n\n**Tables:**\n\n1. **tenants** - Multi-tenant company data\n   - location_id (PK), company_name, client_id, client_secret\n   - access_token, refresh_token, token_expires_at\n   - zapi_instance_id, zapi_token, zapi_client_token\n   - conversation_provider_id, is_active, created_at\n\n2. **ai_agents** - AI configuration per tenant\n   - id (PK), location_id (FK, unique), name, prompt, model\n   - api_key (OpenRouter), elevenlabs_api_key, elevenlabs_voice_id\n   - elevenlabs_speed, elevenlabs_stability, elevenlabs_similarity\n   - groq_api_key (for Whisper), is_active, debounce_seconds\n   - created_at, updated_at\n\n3. **knowledge_documents** - Knowledge base files\n   - id (PK), tenant_id (FK), filename, file_type, blob_url, is_indexed\n   - created_at, updated_at\n\n4. **chat_histories** - Chat memory for AI conversations\n   - id (PK), session_id, message_type (human/ai/system), content\n   - created_at\n\n5. **contact_mappings** - Phone → GHL contact ID mapping\n   - id (PK), location_id, phone_or_lid, ghl_contact_id, created_at\n\n6. **message_mappings** - Z-API messageId ↔ GHL messageId\n   - zapi_message_id (PK), ghl_message_id, location_id, status\n   - created_at\n\n7. **system_settings** - Global system configuration\n   - id (PK), admin_openrouter_key, admin_openrouter_model, updated_at\n\n---\n\n### 4. DEPENDENCIES (requirements.txt)\n\n```\nfastapi==0.115.0\nuvicorn[standard]==0.30.0\nhttpx==0.27.0\napscheduler==3.10.4\npython-dotenv==1.0.1\npydantic>=2.9.0\npydantic-settings>=2.10.1\njinja2==3.1.4\npython-multipart==0.0.9\nsqlalchemy==2.0.35\nalembic==1.13.3\npsycopg2-binary>=2.9.9\nlangchain==1.2.10\nlangchain-classic==1.0.2\nlangchain-community==0.4.1\nlangchain-core==1.2.17\nlangchain-openai==1.1.10\nlangchain-text-splitters==1.1.1\n```\n\n**Stack Summary:**\n- Backend: FastAPI + Uvicorn\n- Database: PostgreSQL (psycopg2-binary)\n- Migrations: Alembic\n- ORM: SQLAlchemy 2.0\n- AI/LLM: LangChain + OpenRouter\n- Voice: ElevenLabs (TTS), Groq Whisper (STT)\n- WhatsApp: Z-API\n- CRM: GoHighLevel\n- Async HTTP: httpx\n\n---\n\n### 5. KEY FEATURES & IMPLEMENTATION DETAILS\n\n**Authentication & Multi-Tenancy:**\n- OAuth 2.0 flow with GHL (GoHighLevel)\n- Token auto-refresh every 12 hours via APScheduler\n- Cookie-based admin dashboard authentication\n\n**AI Agent Engine:**\n- LangChain + ChatOpenAI via OpenRouter\n- PostgreSQL-backed chat memory (PostgresChatMessageHistory)\n- Prompt improvement system (3-step Master AI)\n- Audio transcription via Groq Whisper (STT)\n- Audio response via ElevenLabs (TTS) with configurable voice settings\n- Smart fallback: audio→text if response contains special content (URLs, R$, CPF, etc.)\n- Debounce mechanism: combines rapid messages before AI processing\n\n**Webhook Flows:**\n1. **GHL → Z-API (Outbound):** Message sent in GHL → forwarded to WhatsApp via Z-API\n2. **Z-API → GHL (Inbound):** WhatsApp message received → processed by AI agent → response sent back to GHL\n\n**Dashboard:**\n- Admin login with HMAC-based session tokens\n- Tenant management\n- AI agent configuration (prompt, model, keys, voice settings)\n- Prompt analyzer & improvement with Master AI\n- Chat tester for live agent testing\n- Master AI iterative feedback chat\n\n---\n\n### 6. ISSUES, OBSERVATIONS & POTENTIAL PROBLEMS\n\n**Positive Aspects:**\n- Clean separation of concerns (routers, services, data layers)\n- Proper error handling with try/finally blocks\n- Idempotent database migrations using `_column_exists()` checks\n- Type hints throughout (Python 3.10+ annotations)\n- Environment configuration via pydantic-settings\n\n**Observations & Potential Issues:**\n\n1. **CORS Configuration Warning** (main.py:85-90)\n   - If `ALLOWED_ORIGINS` is not set and `DEBUG=false`, CORS will block cross-origin requests\n   - Current code logs warning but still permits all origins if DEBUG=true\n\n2. **No Test Files Found**\n   - No `tests/` directory or `test_*.py` files in the codebase\n   - No test instructions in `.ralph/AGENT.md` (marked \"No test command configured\")\n\n3. **Chat History Architecture**\n   - Uses SQLAlchemy directly in `PostgresChatMessageHistory` (not async)\n   - Loads full history synchronously during AI request processing\n   - Could be bottleneck with large conversation histories\n\n4. **Session Management**\n   - Admin dashboard uses simple HMAC cookie token (no expiration handling visible)\n   - Cookie max_age set to 30 days\n\n5. **Error Handling Patterns**\n   - Some endpoints use `return` instead of raising HTTPException\n   - Inconsistent error response formats across endpoints\n\n6. **File Organization**\n   - `template_agenteia/` directory exists but purpose unclear\n   - `scripts/` directory exists but content not examined\n\n7. **Migrations Chain**\n   - Migration 004 (ElevenLabs voice settings) exists but not yet reviewed in models.py\n   - All migrations use safe idempotent patterns\n\n8. **Async/Await Usage**\n   - Main.py runs sync Alembic operations in async context (during lifespan)\n   - ChatHistory uses sync SessionLocal in async AI engine\n\n9. **No Type Annotations in Some Places**\n   - Some Pydantic models in admin/ai_agent.py use basic BaseModel without field validation\n\n10. **README.md Notes**\n    - Documentation references `/data/tenants/*.json` but current schema uses database\n    - README may be outdated relative to current PostgreSQL-based implementation\n\n---\n\n### 7. MAIN.PY STRUCTURE\n\n```\n1. Imports (FastAPI, middleware, schedulers, routes)\n2. APScheduler setup for token refresh\n3. Lifespan context manager:\n   - Create all tables via SQLAlchemy\n   - Apply Alembic migrations\n   - Start scheduler\n   - Run initial token refresh\n4. FastAPI app instantiation with CORS configuration\n5. Route registration (5 routers)\n6. Static file mounting\n7. Health endpoints: `/`, `/health`\n8. Uvicorn runner\n```\n\n---\n\n### 8. ALEMBIC MIGRATIONS STATUS\n\n**Current Chain (HEAD → 004):**\n\n| ID | Description | Safe | Status |\n|----|-------------|------|--------|\n| 001 | Add missing columns + system_settings | Idempotent | Applied |\n| 002 | Add debounce_seconds | Idempotent | Applied |\n| 003 | Add groq_api_key | Idempotent | Applied |\n| 004 | Add ElevenLabs voice settings | Not reviewed | Pending |\n\nAll migrations use `_column_exists()` and `_table_exists()` helper functions for safety.\n\n---\n\n### 9. ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES (.env.example)\n\n```\nGHL_CLIENT_ID, GHL_CLIENT_SECRET, GHL_REDIRECT_URI\nGHL_CONVERSATION_PROVIDER_ID\nDATABASE_URL (postgresql://...)\nHOST, PORT\nZAPI_WEBHOOK_SECRET\nLOG_LEVEL\nALLOWED_ORIGINS (NEW - for CORS)\nDEBUG (NEW - for security & reload)\n```\n\n---\n\n### 10. CURRENT STATE & RECOMMENDATIONS\n\n**Health Status:** HEALTHY with minor observations\n\n**Recently Fixed Issues (from git history):**\n- CORS security restriction via env var ✓\n- Master AI prompt truncation issues ✓\n- Chat history not being used by LLM ✓\n- Audio STT/TTS flows ✓\n\n**Recommended Next Actions:**\n1. Add comprehensive test suite for core services\n2. Document the 004 migration (ElevenLabs settings)\n3. Review async/sync boundary issues in ChatHistory loading\n4. Update README.md with current database architecture\n5. Consider adding request validation in Pydantic models\n6. Add integration tests for webhook flows\n\n---\n\n**Files Summary:**\n- Total Python files (excluding venv): ~40 core files\n- Largest files: zapi_receiver.py (403 lines), ghl_service.py (355 lines), ai_service.py (326 lines)\n- Total commits: 15 recent (active development, mostly features + security fixes)\n- Current branch: ralph/tasks (AI agent working on improvements)"}],"totalDurationMs":70850,"totalTokens":58770,"totalToolUseCount":47,"usage":{"input_tokens":7,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1129,"cache_read_input_tokens":54292,"output_tokens":3342,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1129},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
